    • 方法详细资料

      • put

        public V put(K key,
             V value)
        Works like the overriden method, except that null is returned, if the given element could not be added due to map limitations.
        指定者:
        put 在接口中 java.util.Map<K,V>
        覆盖:
        put 在类中 java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentHashMap<K,V>
        参数:
        key - key-value
        value - the associated value
        返回:
        the previous value associated with key, or null if there was no mapping for key, or null if the bounds limit was reached

      • putIfAbsent

        public V putIfAbsent(K key,
                     V value)
        Works like the overriden method, except that null is returned, if the given element could not be added due to map limitations.
        指定者:
        putIfAbsent 在接口中 java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentMap<K,V>
        指定者:
        putIfAbsent 在接口中 java.util.Map<K,V>
        覆盖:
        putIfAbsent 在类中 java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentHashMap<K,V>
        参数:
        key - key-value
        value - the associated value
        返回:
        the previous value or null
